The second season of Hataraku Maou-sama! Sadao Maou returns for more shifts, now having to take care of a small girl born from a golden apple! (Source: Crunchyroll)

The third season of Log Horizon. It’s been a year since Shiroe and his friends were trapped in Akiba due to the Catastrophe. Their forging of the Round Table has brought order and prosperity to its people. But fracturing political alliances and the constant menace of the Genius monsters threaten to destabilize all they’ve fought for and built. Can faith be restored and they persevere, or is its destruction truly inevitable? (Source: Funimation)
Akuyaku Reijou wa Kiraware Kizoku ni Koi wo Suru

Aikawa Eri dies in a traffic accident after staying up all night playing an otome game. She reincarnates as Eris, the villainess of her favorite game. In order to avoid the bad end, she tries her best to change the story, but as expected, it’s hard to rewrite fate…
She is abandoned by the prince. Even more, her life almost ends when she is attacked by a gang of thugs, but a young man appears...
Will the antisocial prince change her destiny? This is the reincarnated villainess’s rebirth romance fantasy!
Totsuide kita Yome Aisouwarai Bakari Shiteru

A Samurai is worried about the fact that his wife always seems to wear a forced smile whenever she's with him. Note: initially self-published on the author's Twitter it later became serialized on Nico Nico Seiga where the story continued.
